---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>

  <!-- ========== LUXURY ========== -->
  <section id="luxury"
           class="min-h-screen grid md:grid-cols-2 place-items-center
                  bg-[#F5EFE6] text-[#3B3A36]">
    <!-- Left: Headline -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end text-center md:text-right p-8">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-serif text-[#BFA06A] mb-6">
        Luxury
      </h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Paragraph -->
    <div class="max-w-xl p-8">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Luxury is a quiet statement of excellence. It lives in
        the textures we touch and the details we notice—an artful
        fusion of refinement and comfort that turns the everyday
        into something extraordinary.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== DISCIPLINE ========== -->
  <section id="discipline"
           class="min-h-screen grid md:grid-cols-2 place-items-center
                  bg-gray-100 text-gray-700">
    <!-- Left: Paragraph -->
    <div class="max-w-xl p-8 order-2 md:order-1">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Discipline is the engine of lasting achievement. It is the
        patient commitment to precision and practice—the invisible
        force that transforms ambition into a legacy of excellence.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Headline -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left p-8 order-1 md:order-2">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-6">
        Discipline
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== ELEGANCE ========== -->
  <section id="elegance"
           class="min-h-screen grid md:grid-cols-2 place-items-center
                  bg-white text-gray-800">
    <!-- Left: Headline -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end text-center md:text-right p-8">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-6">
        Elegance
      </h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Paragraph -->
    <div class="max-w-xl p-8">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Elegance is the art of simplicity perfected. It emerges from
        balance, proportion and a quiet confidence—leaving a lasting
        impression without ever needing to shout.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
